title: Re-Loader 1.4 RC4 Windows Office Activator
description:
This is application the loader activation all versions of the Microsoft Windows and the Microsoft Office. This Tool can be usedf for evaluation purposes ONLY.

* Requirements .NET Framework 4.0
- Install OEM Logo's
- Activate Windows XP/Vista/7/8/8.1/10/Server 2008 (R2)/Server 2012 (R2)/Server TP
- Activate Office 2010/2013/2016
